            <CardTitle>Adjusting BMR</CardTitle>
            <br />
            <p>
                <ul><strong>Building Muscle:</strong> Engaging in resistance training can increase muscle mass, which may elevate BMR.</ul>
                <ul><strong>Healthy Eating:</strong> Adequate nutrition supports metabolism, while severe calorie restriction can decrease BMR.</ul>
                <ul><strong>Physical Activity:</strong> Regular aerobic and strength training can help maintain a higher metabolic rate.</ul>
            </p>
        </Card>
